<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to 1Cause</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fa;
            color: #222;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            background: #0077B6;
            color: white;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar .login-btn {
            background: white;
            color: #0077B6;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .navbar .login-btn:hover {
            background: #005F99;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 90vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 158, 219, 0.8), rgba(0, 58, 100, 0.9)), url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?charity,helping');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background: #005F99;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            background: #004377;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
        }

        .about h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about p {
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            color: #444;
        }

        /* Model UN Links */
        .mun-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .mun-links a {
            background: #0077B6;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .mun-links a:hover {
            background: #005F99;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #0077B6;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">1Cause</div>
        <a href="<%= login_path %>" class="login-btn">Login/Sign Up</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Empowering Change Through AI & Giving</h1>
        <p>Join 1Cause, a revolutionary platform that connects donors directly to real-world causes, ensuring  contributions make the biggest possible impact, with no room for fraud. 1Cause ensures that money goes directly to those who need it most.</p>
        <a href="#about" class="cta-btn">Learn More</a>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about" id="about">
        <h2>How We Make a Difference</h2>
        <p>We use AI to analyze global issues in real-time and direct funding to where it matters most. Our platform enables donors to contribute transparently, without a middle man with interests in profit while supporting UN-backed initiatives, including climate and humanitarian issues.</p>
        
        <!-- Model UN Links -->
        <div class="mun-links">
            <a href="https://www.unrefugees.org/emergencies/" target="_blank">UN Current Global Issues</a>
            <a href="https://www.un.org/en/global-issues/crisis-and-emergency-response" target="_blank">How the UN responds to crises</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>Â© 2025 1Cause | Empowering Change</footer>

</body>
</html>
